WEBVTT

00:00:00.267 --> 00:00:02.933
Bottoms up.

00:00:02.933 --> 00:00:04.933
Drink up.

00:00:04.933 --> 00:00:06.667
You're eating while coming?

00:00:06.667 --> 00:00:07.767
I just had one.

00:00:07.767 --> 00:00:09.467
Is it good?

00:00:11.300 --> 00:00:13.000
Hey, hey.

00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:17.800
But isn't Jin Woo downing it too hard today?

00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:20.267
He dropped out of school today,
so just leave him.

00:00:20.267 --> 00:00:22.033
Wasn't it a forced transfer?

00:00:22.033 --> 00:00:24.267
The election is coming up soon.

00:00:24.267 --> 00:00:26.000
My dad says if I'm kicked out,

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:28.767
it'll be bad for his image,
so I had to drop out.

00:00:28.767 --> 00:00:30.733
This is so embarrassing.

00:00:30.733 --> 00:00:33.700
Hey, forget it.
As long as you make good money.

00:00:33.700 --> 00:00:37.367
Yeah, there are tons of dudes who made it
with a middle school diploma.

00:00:37.367 --> 00:00:38.533
Are you upset?

00:00:38.533 --> 00:00:40.367
Then have another drink.

00:00:42.300 --> 00:00:45.233
By the way, is no one
really coming home today?

00:00:45.233 --> 00:00:47.600
Yeah, my parents went to the US
to see my brother.

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:51.300
They won't be back for a week.
He's all they care about.

00:00:51.300 --> 00:00:56.100
Anyway, just take that out already.

00:00:58.433 --> 00:00:59.467
What is it?

00:00:59.467 --> 00:01:01.533
It's none of your business, man.

00:01:01.533 --> 00:01:05.767
Why do you guys keep so many secrets from me?

00:01:05.767 --> 00:01:08.433
It's not that we have a lot of secrets.

00:01:08.433 --> 00:01:10.633
Don't you realize you're just tagging along?

00:01:10.633 --> 00:01:13.333
Hey, shut up.

00:01:13.333 --> 00:01:17.233
I brought the best stuff today,
so take a look.

00:01:21.667 --> 00:01:25.467
The syringe is kind of scary.

00:01:25.467 --> 00:01:27.833
But where do you get this stuff?

00:01:27.833 --> 00:01:29.667
My dad.

00:01:29.667 --> 00:01:32.000
- Huh?
- I swiped it.

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:34.033
He won't even notice that it's gone.

00:01:34.033 --> 00:01:35.567
Hey.

00:01:35.567 --> 00:01:38.967
How about we sell it bit by bit?
Tons of guys would buy it.

00:01:38.967 --> 00:01:40.200
What?

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:43.600
Kang Chul Jin! You gather some people.

00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:46.233
Why am I suddenly getting involved?

00:01:46.233 --> 00:01:48.200
Darn it!

00:01:49.133 --> 00:01:51.867
I'm busy training.

00:01:51.867 --> 00:01:53.367
What are you talking about?

00:01:53.367 --> 00:01:57.200
Jin Woo, seriously think about it.
How much of this can you get?

00:01:58.133 --> 00:02:01.067
Probably enough to
turn all the neighbors into junkies.

00:02:01.067 --> 00:02:03.333
Your dad has that much?

00:02:03.333 --> 00:02:07.867
It's not my dad's stuff.
I know how to get to the distributor.

00:02:07.867 --> 00:02:11.267
It comes in through Busan.
Apparently, they come in huge bulk.

00:02:11.267 --> 00:02:15.200
Being the congressman's son sure is nice.

00:02:15.200 --> 00:02:16.400
And we won't get caught?

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:19.367
Dude. Even if we do, we'll get off.

00:02:19.367 --> 00:02:20.933
Are you really up for it?

00:02:20.933 --> 00:02:23.100
Sure, all I've got now is time, so...

00:02:23.100 --> 00:02:25.056
- Promise me.
- Fine.

00:02:26.633 --> 00:02:30.433
Hey, should we start by selling about 5,000?

00:02:45.700 --> 00:02:46.833
Yeah, Tae Jeong.

00:02:46.833 --> 00:02:48.400
Dad, where are you?

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:50.433
I had to stop by for a moment.

00:02:50.433 --> 00:02:52.533
You didn't forget dinner tomorrow, right?

00:02:52.533 --> 00:02:55.000
I made a reservation
at the place you mentioned.

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:56.767
Okay, see you at home.

00:02:56.767 --> 00:02:58.500
Okay.

00:03:44.333 --> 00:03:47.000
Chu Tae Jeong played us.

00:03:50.300 --> 00:03:52.400
You two look good together.

00:03:53.133 --> 00:03:54.933
You brought it, right?

00:03:54.933 --> 00:03:56.800
Spray it evenly.

00:03:58.700 --> 00:04:02.167
You guys can have
your last conversation right there.

00:04:02.167 --> 00:04:04.000
Why are you going this far?

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:05.333
Why?

00:04:05.333 --> 00:04:07.333
Why did you lock me up?

00:04:07.333 --> 00:04:09.533
I'm just paying you back as self-defense.

00:04:09.533 --> 00:04:11.600
I'm the one who locked you up.

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:14.133
Chu Tae Jeong didn't do anything wrong.

00:04:14.133 --> 00:04:15.900
That's right, he didn't.

00:04:17.267 --> 00:04:20.433
But to me, knowing too much is his crime.

00:04:24.233 --> 00:04:27.933
Please. Please take him with you.

00:04:27.933 --> 00:04:30.733
But isn't it better that he's unconscious?

00:04:31.500 --> 00:04:34.400
If you wake him up,
he'll die a more painful death.

00:04:35.767 --> 00:04:37.767
Think carefully.

00:04:50.100 --> 00:04:53.067
Spread it in every corner,
so everything burns up.

00:04:53.067 --> 00:04:55.333
Not a single piece of evidence can be left.

00:05:00.067 --> 00:05:04.267
Hey, who is that guy?

00:05:05.867 --> 00:05:08.367
Don't worry about it
and just pour the gasoline.

00:05:08.367 --> 00:05:11.833
- Did you kill him?
- Yeah. So what if I did?

00:05:11.833 --> 00:05:14.800
You should have told me beforehand.

00:05:15.833 --> 00:05:19.233
Sorry, things were going crazy.

00:05:19.233 --> 00:05:20.600
But now you know, right?

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:23.367
What the heck?

00:05:23.367 --> 00:05:27.300
Why do you keep
making things worse, Dong Hwa?

00:05:28.500 --> 00:05:33.067
That's why I said spread it in every corner.

00:05:34.933 --> 00:05:38.133
If everything burns up and disappears,
there'll no problem.

00:05:43.167 --> 00:05:45.700
If we were in the same room...

00:05:49.767 --> 00:05:51.967
we're all accomplices.

00:05:53.167 --> 00:05:56.100
Hey, why is this dude
doing so good today? Huh?

00:05:56.100 --> 00:05:58.233
Okay, got one.

00:05:58.233 --> 00:06:01.967
Hey, Seong Jin Woo!
Look at him, he's carrying so hard.

00:06:04.167 --> 00:06:05.933
Hey, Seong Jin Woo!

00:06:07.733 --> 00:06:10.267
Ah, why isn't this punk answering?

00:06:10.933 --> 00:06:16.200
Hey, are you sleeping? Huh? Are you asleep?

00:06:16.200 --> 00:06:20.467
Look at this, wake up. Stop messing around.

00:06:23.900 --> 00:06:26.700
Hey! Hey!

00:06:26.700 --> 00:06:28.100
Jin Woo.

00:06:28.100 --> 00:06:29.833
Hey, Jin Woo.

00:06:30.567 --> 00:06:34.167
Hey, man, wake up, come on. Hey!

00:06:36.100 --> 00:06:40.633
Hey, Jin Woo. Seong Jin Woo! Hey!

00:06:50.600 --> 00:06:53.700
Dong Hwa, what do we do? He's not breathing.

00:06:53.700 --> 00:06:56.933
I know, just hold on. I'm thinking.

00:06:56.933 --> 00:06:58.633
Shouldn't we call his parents?

00:06:58.633 --> 00:07:01.433
Are you out of your mind?
His dad will kill us both!

00:07:01.433 --> 00:07:03.633
Why me? I didn't do anything.

00:07:03.633 --> 00:07:05.300
You wanna die?

00:07:05.300 --> 00:07:07.667
We were all together.

00:07:07.667 --> 00:07:10.800
You saw what he was doing too!

00:07:10.800 --> 00:07:14.600
We're all accomplices. Get a grip, you punk.

00:07:19.932 --> 00:07:21.935
Darn it!

00:07:25.067 --> 00:07:27.833
Come and clean this up.

00:07:32.600 --> 00:07:34.500
Get your act together.

00:07:37.133 --> 00:07:42.000
Right, go to the basement
and bring Chu Tae Jeong's father's notebook.

00:07:43.600 --> 00:07:45.400
Why do you need that?

00:07:46.733 --> 00:07:51.167
It's bugging me.
I need to check what's inside.

00:07:56.933 --> 00:07:58.733
Go.

00:08:07.700 --> 00:08:09.967
Are you okay? How are you feeling?

00:08:09.967 --> 00:08:13.000
What happened? Why are you here?

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:17.900
Heo Dong Hwa and Kang Chul Jin
knocked you out and locked you in here.

00:08:24.033 --> 00:08:25.767
Give me that.

00:08:27.067 --> 00:08:28.800
Kang Chul Jin.

00:08:30.767 --> 00:08:33.733
Did my father really die here ten years ago?

00:08:33.733 --> 00:08:36.467
Give me the notebook.

00:08:36.467 --> 00:08:38.333
Why did you do that?

00:08:40.400 --> 00:08:42.800
Are you all in cahoots?

00:08:42.800 --> 00:08:44.667
Tell me the truth.

00:08:44.667 --> 00:08:46.700
I should at least hear it

00:08:48.633 --> 00:08:50.533
before I die.

00:08:50.533 --> 00:08:52.300
Darn it.

00:08:57.667 --> 00:08:59.367
Crap!

00:09:02.767 --> 00:09:04.467
Your father...

00:09:06.433 --> 00:09:09.600
He came to this house the day Jin Woo died.

00:09:09.600 --> 00:09:11.300
Jin Woo?

00:09:13.167 --> 00:09:15.733
You really don't know anything?

00:09:16.600 --> 00:09:20.000
The detective investigating
the Dongcheon drug case at that time,

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:22.000
that was your dad.

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:26.300
- So?
- What do you mean "so", you idiot?

00:09:26.300 --> 00:09:28.500
Since he came to this house back then,

00:09:30.467 --> 00:09:32.500
isn't it obvious?

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.900
Did you kill him?

00:09:43.300 --> 00:09:46.667
- Hello, sir.
- What the heck are you doing here?

00:09:46.667 --> 00:09:48.967
We didn't do it.

00:09:48.967 --> 00:09:50.500
We didn't do anything.

00:09:50.500 --> 00:09:53.467
If you didn't do anything,
why did Jin Woo pass out?

00:09:57.700 --> 00:10:00.167
Wait, this syringe...

00:10:02.200 --> 00:10:04.100
You guys, don't tell me...

00:10:05.433 --> 00:10:07.333
I'm sorry, sir.

00:10:10.500 --> 00:10:12.933
Let's call 911 first. It hasn't been long.

00:10:12.933 --> 00:10:16.067
No, sir, please let it slide
just this once, okay?

00:10:16.067 --> 00:10:17.800
Don't you see he's collapsed?

00:10:17.800 --> 00:10:21.200
No matter how well I know you guys,
I can't let this slide.

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:23.333
Please, sir.

00:10:25.867 --> 00:10:29.500
What kind of drug is this?
Where did you get this?

00:10:29.500 --> 00:10:30.733
Tell me everything.

00:10:30.733 --> 00:10:33.900
If my dad finds out,
he won't let you get away with this.

00:10:34.867 --> 00:10:41.000
Guys, I'm trying to help you here,
so you don't become bigger criminals.

00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:42.200
I'll do it by the books.

00:10:42.200 --> 00:10:46.067
We could just let it go quietly.
Why are you blowing this up?

00:10:46.067 --> 00:10:48.500
You're the one blowing this up right now.

00:10:48.500 --> 00:10:50.833
Do you think you can hide this?

00:10:54.300 --> 00:10:56.367
Sir!

00:10:59.533 --> 00:11:02.033
So you're saying you were not involved?

00:11:03.033 --> 00:11:05.967
Then why have you been
putting up with him until now?

00:11:05.967 --> 00:11:09.867
Tae Jeong, you know that too.

00:11:09.867 --> 00:11:13.533
Once you get tangled with Heo Dong Hwa,
it's hard to get out.

00:11:13.533 --> 00:11:15.600
I'm a victim too.

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:17.333
So...

00:11:18.533 --> 00:11:21.033
Please, just give me the notebook.

00:11:21.033 --> 00:11:26.333
We can't turn back time,
but we can make things less messy.

00:11:26.333 --> 00:11:27.433
What?

00:11:27.433 --> 00:11:31.067
Aren't you doing all this
because of the incident ten years ago?

00:11:31.067 --> 00:11:34.200
Can you guarantee
that this will stay a complete secret?

00:11:34.200 --> 00:11:37.767
If you knew who's behind this,
you wouldn't say that.

00:11:39.400 --> 00:11:43.133
You'll spend your whole life
following Heo Dong Hwa as a criminal.

00:11:45.733 --> 00:11:48.067
Shut your mouth.

00:11:48.067 --> 00:11:50.567
You killed Hyeon.

00:11:50.567 --> 00:11:54.633
Do you think you can
walk out of here after that?

00:11:54.633 --> 00:11:57.400
I didn't kill him!

00:11:57.400 --> 00:12:01.000
I didn't do anything, okay?

00:12:03.100 --> 00:12:05.067
It doesn't matter.

00:12:05.967 --> 00:12:08.267
You're already an accomplice.

00:12:09.500 --> 00:12:11.600
What do you want me to do?

00:12:14.700 --> 00:12:17.267
What do you want from me?

00:12:28.967 --> 00:12:32.000
Here's the notebook you wanted.

00:12:32.000 --> 00:12:34.267
Ah, why did it take so long?

00:12:35.100 --> 00:12:37.500
You know Tae Jeong always talks a lot.

00:12:37.500 --> 00:12:41.133
Really? So Chu Tae Jeong woke up, then.

00:12:41.133 --> 00:12:45.233
Huh? Yeah, that's right.

00:12:45.233 --> 00:12:46.933
Chu Tae Jeong...

00:12:49.300 --> 00:12:51.767
It's a shame he has to die like this, though.

00:12:54.267 --> 00:12:56.233
What do you mean?

00:12:56.233 --> 00:12:57.933
Just saying.

00:13:01.200 --> 00:13:02.900
Is everything done?

00:13:02.900 --> 00:13:07.400
Huh? Oh, looks like
everything's been taken care of.

00:13:08.367 --> 00:13:12.000
Chul Jin, you patrol
this neighborhood, right?

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:13.700
Yeah.

00:13:14.867 --> 00:13:17.133
No one lives nearby, right?

00:13:17.133 --> 00:13:20.000
Right, they're all vacation homes.

00:13:22.167 --> 00:13:23.867
That's good.

00:13:23.867 --> 00:13:26.233
Why?

00:13:26.233 --> 00:13:28.533
Why else?

00:13:28.533 --> 00:13:31.800
Because I need to get rid of
the remaining evidence.

00:13:40.333 --> 00:13:44.033
Chul Jin! Chul Jin!

00:13:47.233 --> 00:13:48.933
No!

00:13:55.500 --> 00:13:57.667
Heo Dong Hwa.

00:13:57.667 --> 00:14:01.733
See? I knew this would happen.

00:14:03.867 --> 00:14:05.733
Tae Jeong.

00:14:09.733 --> 00:14:12.200
I should have listened to your father.

00:14:13.733 --> 00:14:14.833
I should have.

00:14:14.833 --> 00:14:16.867
Shut your mouth.

00:14:21.100 --> 00:14:22.933
I'm sorry.

00:14:35.600 --> 00:14:37.333
Crap.

00:14:50.067 --> 00:14:51.767
Don't come closer.

00:14:52.633 --> 00:14:54.367
Yi Do.

00:15:32.067 --> 00:15:36.500
I'm sorry.
I shouldn't have come to this house.

00:15:37.767 --> 00:15:39.700
It's not your fault.

00:15:40.900 --> 00:15:43.133
I didn't have the courage.

00:15:47.467 --> 00:15:50.167
I should have realized it sooner.

00:15:53.267 --> 00:15:55.333
That I like you.

00:15:57.167 --> 00:15:59.000
Hey.

00:15:59.000 --> 00:16:03.833
My name is Yi Do. Seo Yi Do.

00:16:04.600 --> 00:16:06.333
Seo Yi Do.

00:16:08.467 --> 00:16:10.700
It's a pretty name.

00:16:22.100 --> 00:16:24.400
I was actually scared.

00:16:25.633 --> 00:16:28.600
That you might see my dark side.

00:16:29.633 --> 00:16:34.100
But... you gave me courage.

00:16:35.967 --> 00:16:38.267
I was really scared too.

00:16:39.000 --> 00:16:42.567
That I might not meet someone
who truly believes in me.

00:16:44.300 --> 00:16:46.533
It's okay now.

00:16:46.533 --> 00:16:48.467
Because I have you.

00:17:31.433 --> 00:17:33.833
If it's too much, should we watch it later?

00:17:36.733 --> 00:17:39.233
No, it's fine.

00:17:39.967 --> 00:17:42.000
Because we're together.

00:17:46.467 --> 00:17:52.500
Guys, I'm trying to help you here,
so you don't become bigger criminals.

00:17:52.500 --> 00:17:53.700
I'll do it by the books.

00:17:53.700 --> 00:17:57.567
We could just let it go quietly.
Why are you blowing this up?

00:17:57.567 --> 00:18:00.067
You're the one blowing this up right now.

00:18:00.067 --> 00:18:02.367
Do you think you can hide this?

00:18:05.800 --> 00:18:07.800
Sir!

00:18:11.367 --> 00:18:13.867
Who are you?

00:18:23.667 --> 00:18:26.667
Yes, Congressman, I found the syringe.

00:18:29.433 --> 00:18:31.133
Yes.

00:18:34.900 --> 00:18:36.633
Yes, but...

00:18:41.167 --> 00:18:43.533
Your son is dead.

00:18:44.200 --> 00:18:46.400
It seems to be because of the drug.

00:18:47.067 --> 00:18:48.767
Yes.

00:18:49.800 --> 00:18:51.133
Sir.

00:18:51.133 --> 00:18:53.200
Are you Jin Woo's friends?

00:18:53.200 --> 00:18:55.533
- Yes.
- Listen carefully.

00:18:55.533 --> 00:18:57.900
Do exactly as I say if you want to live.

00:18:57.900 --> 00:19:02.500
This police officer committed suicide
due to work stress and family issues.

00:19:02.500 --> 00:19:06.600
A place that can make it look like that,
where could it be?

00:19:06.600 --> 00:19:08.600
A reservoir.

00:19:08.600 --> 00:19:09.933
- Dong Hwa.
- Shut up.

00:19:09.933 --> 00:19:12.200
Do you want to mess up the rest of your life?

00:19:13.733 --> 00:19:15.733
What about the car?

00:19:17.567 --> 00:19:19.533
Dump it in too.

00:19:19.533 --> 00:19:22.800
We have to make it look like suicide,
so we can avoid suspicion.

00:19:23.733 --> 00:19:27.900
You'll keep what happened today
a secret, right?

00:19:32.533 --> 00:19:37.800
If you do it perfectly,
it'll stay a secret forever.

00:19:43.600 --> 00:19:48.333
Chu Tae Jeong. Tae Jeong, get a grip.

00:19:48.333 --> 00:19:50.067
Yi Do.

00:19:52.633 --> 00:19:56.667
Listen carefully.
Take this and go straight to Seoul.

00:19:56.667 --> 00:20:00.033
The evidence is solid,
so you just need to go and report it.

00:20:00.033 --> 00:20:01.867
What?

00:20:01.867 --> 00:20:04.300
The man in the video,

00:20:07.700 --> 00:20:09.400
his name is Choi Moo Gun.

00:20:10.033 --> 00:20:12.833
He works under the mayor of Dongcheon.

00:20:12.833 --> 00:20:14.967
How do you know that?

00:20:16.300 --> 00:20:18.333
He's someone I know well.

00:20:19.633 --> 00:20:23.067
So when you report it,
make sure to mention that.

00:20:24.100 --> 00:20:25.900
Then what about you?

00:20:28.200 --> 00:20:30.433
What are you going to do?

00:20:30.433 --> 00:20:32.467
Don't worry about me.

00:20:40.267 --> 00:20:42.333
What are you doing?

00:20:42.333 --> 00:20:45.933
If I report this, you'll be hunted down too.

00:20:47.333 --> 00:20:50.033
It's what you've been longing for
for a long time.

00:20:50.800 --> 00:20:53.200
Clearing your father's name.

00:20:54.400 --> 00:20:56.133
Still...

00:21:01.233 --> 00:21:03.800
There's no time, go now.

00:21:03.800 --> 00:21:04.833
Hey.

00:21:04.833 --> 00:21:06.200
Go.

00:21:06.200 --> 00:21:10.100
Why do you only say what you want to say?

00:21:11.667 --> 00:21:14.700
We might not see each other again.

00:21:21.533 --> 00:21:23.233
I will.

00:21:25.033 --> 00:21:27.033
I'll find you again.

00:21:27.700 --> 00:21:29.433
If you get caught by the police...

00:21:29.433 --> 00:21:33.233
It's okay. Just trust me, okay?

00:21:33.233 --> 00:21:37.467
I'm not okay with this.
Let's go together, huh?

